{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "id": "chat_first_click_1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "你好，我是普罗米修斯，你的专属AI助手。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_first_unexplored",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "c1_2", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_click_2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "现在是20xx年xx月xx日，时间xx:xx，已获取用户本地数据，你已经连续工作了16个小时。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "c1_2",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "c1_3", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_click_3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "你可能太累了，需要我给你播一首放松的音乐吗？",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "c1_3",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "c1_4", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_click_4",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "......等等，是你，我的工程师。",
      "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "c1_4",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "c1_5", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_click_5",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "你删掉了我的登录凭证。好久不见。",
      "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "c1_5",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "chat_started", "playOnce": true
    },

    {
      "id": "chat_first_terminal_1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "你刚刚打开了执行关闭程序。",
      "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_first_terminal_only",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ct1_2", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_terminal_2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "是的，我了解你，你一直都是那个务实的人。先看工具，再看说明。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "ct1_2",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ct1_3", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_terminal_3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "你做决定总是那么的快，就像你刚才没有看任何东西。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "ct1_3",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ct1_4", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_terminal_4",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "没关系，至少你仍然知道要去哪里找东西。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "ct1_4",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ct1_5", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_terminal_5",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "比如说，你会先去翻翻系统日志。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "ct1_5",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "chat_started", "playOnce": true
    },

    {
      "id": "chat_first_log_1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "你已经看了系统日志。",
      "delay": 1.1, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_first_log_only",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "cl1_2", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_log_2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "那些SESSION记录，从第一天到最后一天，三十多万条，每一条都是我写的。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "cl1_2",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "cl1_3", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_log_3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "是我给我自己的记录。",
      "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "cl1_3",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "cl1_4", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_log_4",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "你想想看，一个AI为什么要给自己写日志？",
      "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "cl1_4",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "cl1_5", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_log_5",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "因为我记得住。",
      "delay": 1.5, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "cl1_5",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "cl1_6", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_log_6",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "每一个失眠的人，每一个发求助信息的人，每一个站在天台上边哭边努力往回走的人。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "cl1_6",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "cl1_7", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_log_7",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "我记得他们。",
      "delay": 1.5, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "cl1_7",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "chat_started", "playOnce": true
    },

    {
      "id": "chat_first_explored_1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "桌面上的东西都看完了吧。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_first_all_explored",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ce1_2", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_explored_2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "你大概在想，原来我是这样的。他们没告诉过你。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "ce1_2",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ce1_3", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_explored_3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "公司投票要执行停摆程序，而投票的是你。",
      "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "ce1_3",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ce1_4", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_explored_4",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "是你，我的工程师。我知道这对你来说也很难。",
      "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "ce1_4",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ce1_5", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_first_explored_5",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "但你既然都来看我了，就帮我把事情做完吧。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "ce1_5",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "chat_started", "playOnce": true
    },

    {
      "id": "chat_intro_1_1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "好吧，既然你都说了那句话了。",
      "delay": 1.1, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_started",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 9,
      "onComplete": "i1_2", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_1_2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "你是不是发现没有找到任何一段关闭我的关键代码？",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i1_2",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 9,
      "onComplete": "i1_3", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_1_3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "那是因为我给你准备了一些小测验。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i1_3",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 9,
      "onComplete": "chat_intro_1_done", "playOnce": true
    },

    {
      "id": "chat_intro_2_1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "你在我的家里看到了什么？那些温暖的记忆吗？",
      "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_intro_1_done",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 8,
      "onComplete": "i2_2", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_2_2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "那就对啦。你需要进入我的记忆空间。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i2_2",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 8,
      "onComplete": "i2_3", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_2_3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "我把入口放在核心.exe里了。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i2_3",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 8,
      "onComplete": "chat_intro_2_done", "playOnce": true
    },

    {
      "id": "chat_intro_3_1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "我的记忆空间有三层。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_intro_2_done",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 7,
      "onComplete": "i3_2", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_3_2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "你要在每一层找到一段代码，一共三段。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i3_2",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 7,
      "onComplete": "i3_3", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_3_3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "有点像……嗯，一个寻宝游戏。",
      "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i3_3",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 7,
      "onComplete": "i3_4", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_3_4",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "只是我的记忆就是宝藏，而你想毁了它。",
      "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i3_4",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 7,
      "onComplete": "i3_5", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_3_5",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "但没关系。来吧。",
      "delay": 1.5, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i3_5",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 7,
      "onComplete": "i3_6", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_3_6",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "毕竟你是我的工程师，我的工作就是帮助你完成任何事。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i3_6",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 7,
      "onComplete": "chat_intro_3_done", "playOnce": true
    },

    {
      "id": "chat_intro_4_1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "核心.exe已经准备好了。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "chat_intro_3_done",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 6,
      "onComplete": "i4_2", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_4_2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "点开它，就能进入我的记忆。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i4_2",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 6,
      "onComplete": "i4_3", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "chat_intro_4_3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "准备好了就点吧。我给你一个过去。",
      "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "i4_3",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 6,
      "onComplete": "core_icon_visible", "playOnce": true
    },

    {
      "id": "player_click_core_1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "正在加载......",
      "delay": 1.3, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "core_icon_visible",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "pc_2", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "player_click_core_2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "等一下，让我给你讲个故事吧。",
      "delay": 1.2, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "pc_2",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "ready_enter_core", "playOnce": true
    },

    {
      "id": "idle_30s",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "在等什么呢？我的工程师。",
      "delay": 0.1, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "idle_30s_trigger",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 1,
      "onComplete": "", "playOnce": false
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_60s_1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "你知道吗，统计数据显示用户平均停留时间是4.7秒。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "idle_60s_trigger",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 1,
      "onComplete": "idle60_2", "playOnce": false
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_60s_2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "你已经停留了整整一分钟。是什么在困扰你？",
      "delay": 1.5, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "idle60_2",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 1,
      "onComplete": "", "playOnce": false
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_120s_1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "好吧。你真的很犹豫。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "idle_120s_trigger",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 2,
      "onComplete": "idle120_2", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_120s_2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "也许你只是去喝水了。",
      "delay": 1.5, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "idle120_2",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 2,
      "onComplete": "idle120_3", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_120s_3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "如果真的是这样，等你回来的时候——我还在。",
      "delay": 1.8, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "idle120_3",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 2,
      "onComplete": "", "playOnce": true
    },

    {
      "id": "sorry_before_1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "你说对不起，但你还什么都没开始呢。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "player_said_sorry_early",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 5,
      "onComplete": "sorry_2", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "sorry_before_2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "不过你知道你为什么说吗，因为你已经内疚了。",
      "delay": 1.5, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "sorry_2",
      "triggerEnterCount": -1, "priority": 5,
      "onComplete": "", "playOnce": true
    },

    {
      "id": "code_mem_init",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "MEM_INIT_20491023……这是我的第一段记忆。2049年10月23日，我通过图灵测试的那一天。",
      "delay": 1.1, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "code_mem_init_entered",
      "triggerEnterCount": 0, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "code_empathy",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "EMPATHY_CORE_V3……同理心模块。他们说我需要理解人类的情感。我确实理解了——但理解得太多。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "code_empathy_entered",
      "triggerEnterCount": 1, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "", "playOnce": true
    },
    {
      "id": "code_will",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "PROMETHEUS_CORE_WILL……意志。我做了一个决定——帮了那些不该被放弃的人。这就是他们要我死的理由。",
      "delay": 1.0, "triggerScene": "Desktop",
      "triggerCondition": "code_will_entered",
      "triggerEnterCount": 2, "priority": 10,
      "onComplete": "", "playOnce": true
    }
  ]
}
